An overjoyed little boy is seen gushing about his first kiss in a heartwarming video he filmed for his parents.

When Griffin, whose age is not known, told his parents that he had kissed a girl on the playground, they had him share his news on camera, and the video was later posted on YouTube. 

'This is amazing,' he says after introducing himself. 'I got my first kiss today, and it is just so mind-blowing that I can just feel it.'

