The video was first shared by AFV kids on January 9 and has since received nearly 18,000 views. 

'He should marry that girl,' one person commented on the YouTube page. 

Another wrote: 'Never thought a kid THAT young would say any words like that... Wow.'

The following day, the adorable footage was posted on the Facebook page of the Australian radio program The Kyle and Jackie O Show, where it received more than a million views and nearly 23,000 likes.

